Purpose:
--------
Translate between the raw tcp socket of the SceneServerâ„¢ and the provided websocket.
Communication is secured by SSL. Add the Websocketsproxy certificate to your browsers
certificate store to prevent/detect man-in-the-middle attacks.

Changes:
* Fix no-implicit string->ascii converting issue
* write -> writeText, writeBinary method signature changes

Originated from
* https://github.com/ruslansalikhov/QtWebsocket (WSS) [copy from commit# 12223ab8fa8cd609f16cac3cc10f5d4ad0b7326b]
* https://github.com/ant-lafarge/QtWebsocket (Original implementation)